---
const title = "Through the Veil";
const description = "A quiet place. Not everything needs to be explained.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Through the Veil | Jack Bronco</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Through the Veil by Jack Bronco. A supernatural thriller now available on Amazon. Read free with Kindle Unlimited or purchase."
    />
    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="Through the Veil, Jack Bronco, supernatural fiction, horror fiction, action thriller fiction"
    />

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: #0a0a0a;
        color: #eaeaea;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p {
        opacity: 0.7;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        padding: 0.85rem 1.4rem;
        border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        color: #eaeaea;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: #eaeaea;
        color: #0a0a0a;
      }

      .hidden {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(10px);
      }

      .show {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
        transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
      }

      .amazon-proof {
        display: inline-flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #eaeaea;
        max-width: 420px;
      }

      .amazon-proof img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border: 1px solid rgba(234, 234, 234, 0.2);
        border-radius: 6px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .amazon-proof span {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        opacity: 0.55;
      }

      .amazon-proof:hover img {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .blurb {
        display: block;
        text-align: left;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }

</style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <h1 class="hidden" id="pageTitle">Through the Veil</h1>

      <p class="hidden" id="pageText">
        You found it.<br /><br />
        Not everything is meant to be explained right away.<br /><br />
      <span class="blurb">
        The veil between Light and Dark isn’t a myth—it’s real, hidden in plain
        sight on our own Earth.
        <br /><br />
        When Cole stumbles across it and steps through, he discovers too late
        that return isn’t guaranteed.
        <br /><br />
        The two living souls he loves most are left behind on the other side…
        and every path home drags him deeper into a world shaped by shadows,
        predators, and choices with irreversible consequences.
        <br /><br />
        As he searches for a way back, Cole is forced to confront decisions that
        challenge his one driving desire: to return home and reclaim his simple
        life with those he loves.
      </span>      
        <br /><br />
        Some things are meant to be stepped into.
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GCM12FFJ"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="button hidden"
        id="amazonBtn"
      >
        Read Free with KU or Buy on Amazon
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GCM12FFJ"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="amazon-proof hidden"
        id="amazonProof"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/through-the-veil-amazon-preview.jpg"
          alt="Amazon listing preview for Through the Veil by Jack Bronco"
        />
        <span>Amazon listing preview</span>
      </a>
    </main>

    <script>
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById("pageTitle")?.classList.remove("hidden");
        document.getElementById("pageTitle")?.classList.add("show");
      }, 400);

      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById("pageText")?.classList.remove("hidden");
        document.getElementById("pageText")?.classList.add("show");
      }, 1800);

      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById("amazonBtn")?.classList.remove("hidden");
        document.getElementById("amazonBtn")?.classList.add("show");
      }, 3900);

      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById("amazonProof")?.classList.remove("hidden");
        document.getElementById("amazonProof")?.classList.add("show");
      }, 5200);
    </script>
  </body>

</html>
